			</div>
			<!-- Question Row -->
			<div class="row" id="welcome-description">
				<h3 class="colored">How does it work?</h3>
				<p> Triage integrates with a growing number of 3rd party services. Triage monitors what's happening with each service and aggregates everything important to you into your Triage feed.</p>
			</div>
			<!-- Question Row -->
			<div class="row" id="welcome-description">
				<h3 class="colored">How much does it cost? </h3>
				<p> Triage is a free service, and our plan is to keep it that way. In the future, Triage will charge for additional enterprise services.</p>
			</div>
			<!-- Question Row -->
			<div class="row" id="welcome-description">
				<h3 class="colored">Can my whole team use it?</h3>
