			</div>
			<!-- Question Row -->
			<div class="row" id="welcome-description">
				<h3 class="colored">What platforms does Triage support?</h3>
				<p> Triage is available for iOS 7. <br />Tablet, Android and web versions are coming shortly.</p>
			</div>
			<!-- Question Row -->
			<div class="row" id="welcome-description">
				<h3 class="colored">Are my profile and data private? </h3>
				<p>Only active employees at your company with a verified email address can see your Triage data. No activity of yours is shared outside of your company with any third parties. </p>
			</div>
			<!-- Question Row -->
			<div class="row" id="welcome-description">
				<h3 class="colored">Is my data safe with Triage?</h3>
				<p> All traffic is encrypted with SSL/HTTPs, both when receiving data from 3rd party services and again when communicating between the Triage mobile app and servers.</p>
			</div>
			<!-- Question Row -->
			<div class="row" id="welcome-description">
				<h3 class="colored">Can I cancel my account?</h3>
